      </div>
    </div>

    <p>SmartyPants Kids Formula is the most comprehensive children's gummy vitamin available. It includes what most competitors omit: omega-3 DHA and EPA from fish oil for brain development, methylated B12 for superior absorption, and vitamin K2 for bone health alongside vitamin D3. The 15-nutrient profile covers the most critical developmental needs in a single product, reducing the need for multiple supplements. With over 32,000 reviews averaging 4.8 stars, the taste and compliance factor is proven. The B Corp certification and 1-for-1 nutrient grant program mean every bottle purchased funds nutrition for a child in need.</p>

