    <p>Olly combines a comprehensive multivitamin with a heat-stable probiotic strain (Bacillus coagulans) that survives both shelf storage and stomach acid — a significant advantage over probiotics that lose viability during manufacturing and digestion. This dual-action formula supports both nutritional needs and digestive/immune health in a single 2-gummy serving. For parents trying to minimize the number of supplements their child takes, Olly consolidates two products into one. The berry punch flavor consistently ranks among the best-tasting in our kids' testing panel.</p>

    <!-- PRODUCT 3 — GARDEN OF LIFE -->
