    <p>For parents who prioritize the cleanest possible ingredients for their children, Garden of Life's USDA Organic kids' gummy is the gold standard. Every vitamin is sourced from real organic fruits and vegetables — not synthesized in a lab. The formula contains zero artificial colors (which some research links to hyperactivity in sensitive children), zero artificial flavors, and zero synthetic sweeteners. The 800 IU vitamin D3 dose exceeds the AAP recommendation of 600 IU, providing extra protection for the 70% of children with suboptimal vitamin D. The vegan formula uses pectin instead of gelatin, making it suitable for plant-based families.</p>

