    <p>Nature Made's USP Verification is the single most reliable quality indicator in the supplement industry. USP independently tests for potency (label claims match actual content), purity (free of heavy metals and contaminants), and dissolution (the gummy actually breaks down for absorption). For parents concerned about whether a kids' vitamin actually contains what the label claims — a legitimate concern in the loosely regulated supplement industry — USP Verification provides the definitive answer. At $0.22 per serving, it is the most affordable quality-guaranteed option.</p>

    <!-- PRODUCT 5 — VITAFUSION -->
    <div class="pcard" id="vitafusion">
