        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p>When a child absolutely refuses every other vitamin, Vitafusion is the answer. The taste quality is genuinely candy-like — our kids' testing panel rated it first among all 18 products for flavor and willingness to take daily. At $0.17 per serving, it is also the most affordable. The vitamin profile covers the essentials (A, C, D, E, B vitamins), though it lacks omega-3 and probiotics. The practical reality of pediatric supplementation: the best vitamin is the one your child will actually take. If taste and compliance are your primary challenges, Vitafusion solves them.</p>

